<TEXT>&#2;<DATELINE>2000-03-31</DATELINE><TITLE>Differentiation of Gastrointestinal Diseases of Calves</TITLE><BODY>Bovine practitioners are commonly faced with gastrointestinal problems in calves. Being able to diagnose gastrointestinal problems properly is pivotal in developing proper preventive and treatment strategies. This article discusses the common gastrointestinal diseases, including diarrhea of calves, with the focus on antemortem diagnosis and differentiation of these diseases.&#3;</BODY></TEXT>